# Plan Research Report

Read an input document, or prompt, and produce a structured research plan for user approval before any research begins. The plan defines what needs to be investigated.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write the output of this plan to the output path: {{task.changePath}}/plan.md

Once you finish the plan, you MUST output one of the required signals.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

## Process

```dot
digraph plan {
    rankdir=TB;
    read [label="Read input document" shape=box];
    gate [label="Research task?" shape=diamond];
    redirect [label="Tell user to use\naop-task-planner" shape=box];
